interpretation: The oncoming fist is a symbol of power, strength, and assertion. It represents the desire to take action and make an impact. This card suggests that you have the ability to overcome obstacles and challenges in your life with sheer force and determination. It may also indicate a need to stand up for yourself and assert your boundaries in a situation where you feel threatened or powerless. The oncoming fist reminds you to tap into your inner strength and courage, and to take bold action to achieve your goals. However, be mindful of the impact your actions may have on others, and use your power wisely and responsibly. Associated keywords include: assertiveness, courage, force, impact, strength, power, action, determination, and boundaries.
